### Get paginated sessions (limit 10, offset 0)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions?limit=10&offset=0
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all sessions (no pagination)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions?limit=-1
Accept: application/json

###

### Invalid limit (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions?limit=abc&offset=0
Accept: application/json
